FBIS4-59765 "drnes096_j_94018" FBIS-NES-94-096 Daily Report 15 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen ICRC Reaches Agreement on Care for War Captives ICRC Reaches Agreement on Care for War Captives EA1505191194 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 15 May 94 EA1505191194 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] A statement issued by the Cairo office of the International Committee of the Red Cross [ICRC] says that the committee has reached agreements providing for visiting fighters detained by both sides in the dispute. The statement recalled that the committee had already visited a number of captives in Aden. It stressed that representatives of the Red Cross were continuing their efforts to supply medical organizations with basic supplies for the treatment of the war victims.
